user_query: I want to surprise my sister with a cute kitten picture as a gift. Can you find me a high-quality kitten image that I can print and frame? Additionally, provide me with some interesting cat facts that I can write on a card to accompany the picture. Also, suggest a reputable online photo printing service that offers fast delivery.

TaskList.description: Search for a high-quality kitten image suitable for printing.
Retrieve interesting cat facts to accompany the kitten picture.
Evaluate and suggest a reputable online photo printing service with fast delivery options.
Compile the kitten image, cat facts, and printing service information into a presentation format.
